Race.SpecificTitle: City Marshal -- City Court, City of Thibodaux
PW Juvenile Justice Commission -- 3.20 Mills Renewal - BOC - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Parishwide Juvenile Justice Commission Proposition
(Tax Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall the Juvenile Justice Commission of the Parish of Lafourche, State of Louisiana (the "Parish"), levy a tax of three and twenty hundredths (3.20) mills (the "Tax"), on all the property subject to taxation in the Parish (an estimated $3,100,000 reasonably expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2022 and ending with the year 2031, for the purpose of improving, maintaining or operating Juvenile Justice Facilities in the Parish?
